text: Quebec is a 1951 American historical adventure movie directed by George Templeton and starring John Drew Barrymore, Corinne Calvet, Barbara Bush, Patric Knowles, John Hoyt. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1951 adventure movies Category:1950s historical movies Category:American adventure movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies set in the 1830s Category:Movies set in Quebec
